        SKILL                                                                   = 10177,  -- [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert].
        SKILL_SKILL                                                             = 10178,  -- [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert]. [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert].
        SKILL_SKILL_SKILL                                                       = 10179,  -- [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert]. [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert]. [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert].
        SKILL_SKILL_SKILL_SKILL                                                 = 10180,  -- [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert]. [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert]. [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert]. [Fishing/Woodworking/Smithing/Goldsmithing/Clothcraft/Leathercraft/Bonecraft/Alchemy/Cooking/Fishing] skill: [Amateur/Recruit/Initiate/Novice/Apprentice/Journeyman/Craftsman/Artisan/Adept/Veteran/Expert].
